name: Url checker
description:
This is minified URl/I checker, it gives back 9 groups if valid:
1: Whole URL
2: s if SSL is specified
3: URL without https?://www.
4: Subdomains
5: Domain
6: Domain lang
7: Location
8: Query string
9: Hash

sps-prosek.magistri.cz
https://www.sps-prosek.magistri.cz/ahoj/boo?a=5#Ahoj
http://www.sps-prosek.magistri.cz

Sample text for testing:
abcdefghijklmnopqrstuvwxyz ABCDEFGHIJKLMNOPQRSTUVWXYZ
0123456789 +-.,!@#$%^&*();\/|<>"'
12345 -98.7 3.141 .6180 9,000 +42
555.123.4567	+1-(800)-555-2468
foo@demo.net	bar.ba@test.co.uk
www.demo.com	http://foo.co.uk/
http://regexr.com/foo.html?q=bar&foo=big
